{
  "stem": "23498.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was just, you know, schlepping him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I brought him there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She looked after him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She might have bought for him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He-- he had hemorrhoids because from a long sitting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and I was afraid she would-- she didn't recognize.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He didn't look Jewish at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she didn't recognize me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was the-- you know, quite happy, and slowly he came to himself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But what I found out, when he left the Russians, maybe they were the same Russians who were interrogated them and-- and my-- I don't think so, because they were officials.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But some Russians were, you know, stealing the Polish goods.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they came one night, you know, and wanted to steal the goods from them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were rich people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was the Freunds.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Freunds.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Freund started to scream.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of the Russians said, you don't scream because we'll kill you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she started to scream because the-- everything was very precious to-- to her-- the-- the furs and the jewelry and so on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they killed her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they killed her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was really very sorry, because, good or bad about my brother's survival.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Soon after, Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Freund died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was a terrible thing, but he couldn't live without her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He loved her very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the thing is-- that that was when the parents were back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The thing is, when my mother approached the family and said that my brother will have a speech, they said, no.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "None of you is going to the funeral.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was already after the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So, in other words, they-- even those who were doing the good things were afraid of the others, that they will point them out that they helped the Jews.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
